snippet.title: Guild of Dungeoneering: Pirates Cove Adventure Pack Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.gog.com/game/pirates_cove_adventure_pack

Welcome to Pirates Cove!

Pirates Cove includes a new region, new swashbuckling quests, terrifying new enemies, and of course, tons more booty. Come aboard and raise the Jolly Roger for this grand adventure!
